WEBVTT

00:01.755 --> 00:05.038
There's a rule that's written in stone.

00:09.847 --> 00:11.567
Robinsons stick together.

00:15.872 --> 00:16.829
It's not safe out there.

00:16.995 --> 00:18.089
You don't know what you might find.

00:22.255 --> 00:22.577
John?

00:23.466 --> 00:24.064
Where are you?

00:28.603 --> 00:29.267
Who are you?

00:29.653 --> 00:30.550
It's complicated.

00:34.377 --> 00:38.610
If you have any hope of saving your family, you will help me.

00:40.211 --> 00:43.115
Go get our kids and get them off this planet.

